description:
Mythic Adventure Awaits!
Suit up, Bionaut and get ready for an awesome new adventure! The Floating Islands need your help! Save minotaurs, dragons, unicorns and other mythological bankimals! Use your money sense to help Rainbow Cat’s smoothie business to get back up and running again.

FEATURES
•	14 mythical bankimals to save!
•	Ride the magical Unicorn!
•	Glide through the air on a Dragon!
•	Collect golden eggs and plant a giant beanstalk!
name: Fantasy Island
